ChangeSet@1.1633, 2004-03-03 11:50:22+01:00, vojtech@suse.cz
  input: Only do hotplug on PS/2 HW when the HW sends 0xaa. This
         avoids problems with broken USB->PS/2 legacy emulation
         in certain BIOSes.


 serio.c |    3 +++
 1 files changed, 3 insertions(+)

===================================================================

